## WebGPU and friends

# Langs

* GLSL (OpenGL Shading Language)
* SPIR-V (Standard Portable Intermediate Representation)
* WGSL (WebGPU Shading Language)
* HLSL (High-Level Shading Language) DirectX
* PTX (Parallel Thread Execution) CUDA
* Other Metal/openCL

